VALUES (335, 'Neutral Grip Chest Supported Dumbbell Row Video Exercise Guide', 'Upper Back', 'Strength', 'Dumbbell',
        'Compound', 'Pull (Bilateral)', 'Beginner', 'Biceps, Lats, Shoulders', 'The chest supported dumbbell row is a variation of the dumbbell bent over row and an exercise used to build back muscle and strength.
