VALUES (344, 'Thoracic Extension on Foam Roller Video Exercise Guide', 'Upper Back', 'Warmup', 'Foam Roll', 'Isolation',
        'Dynamic Stretching', 'Beginner', 'None', 'The thoracic extension on foam roller drill is a form of dynamic stretching that warms up the muscles of the upper back.
