Drop the hips back to the deep lunge position and ensure the back leg is straight by flexing the quad.
With your hands flat on the floor, exhale, rotate your torso, and reach toward the ceiling with the arm closest to your instep.
Follow your hand with your eyes as you rotate.
Rotate back to the starting position and stand upright again.
Repeat for the desired number of repetitions on each side.', 'As your rotate and reach towards the ceiling, make sure your head and eyes follow your hand.
